ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR SCIENTIFIC SOFTWARE

If you use this software in scientific publications, we request that you:

1. Cite the original paper:
   Barreiro, L. et al. (E-QFT Collaboration), "General Relativity as an 
   Emergent Limit of Quantum Projector Fields", arXiv:2025.XXXXX (2025)

2. Include a link to the software repository:
   https://github.com/E-QFT-Team/E-QFT_e-gravity_v5

3. Acknowledge the E-QFT Collaboration in your acknowledgments section

These are requests, not legal requirements. The software is still fully
open source under GPL-3.0 regardless of whether these requests are followed.